   154	| **Historical data migration scope** | D-5 | **Decided here in System Setup §3.10 D-5** |
   155	
   156	## 3.10.5 Recommendation summary
   157	
   158	The merged-company System Setup playbook in shorthand:
   159	
   160	- **Governance:** DREAM methodology with named-role assignments determined during organizational alignment
   161	- **Cutover strategy:** Soft cutover for both legacy systems, sequenced by process area
