    72	- **Active where possible.** "We state it up front because" not "Stating it up front matters because."
    73	- **Em-dash (—) for parenthetical asides**, with spaces on either side.
    74	- **Section references** use § (U+00A7) — do not write "section" in body text when referencing.
    75	- **Em-dash, en-dash, hyphen** — em-dash for breaks, hyphen for compound words; avoid en-dash unless representing a range.
