     1	# Business Requirements Document - System Setup and Configuration
     2	## Solution Alignment & Validation
     3	
     4	**Document Version**: 1.0  
     5	**Date**: October 23, 2025  
     6	**Process Area**: System Setup and Configuration  
     7	**Implementation Name**: KBM Hoag NetSuite Orion Implementation  
