   458	## <a id="_Toc221888644"></a>3\.04 Native Segmentation
   459	
   460	3\.04\.01 Your Business Requirements
   461	
   462	- __REQ\-3\.04\.01: __Location tracking \(two California locations\)__ __
   463		-  Fremont and La Mirada
