_Unification/08 - Operations.md:189:- **Work orders:** Dual pattern — hard assignment for internal crews; soft scheduling for outsourced contractor coordination
_Unification/08 - Operations.md:190:- **Field Service app:** Deployed for both internal technicians and PM oversight of outsourced contractor work
