99:### D-4. Identity and access management — merged-company role taxonomy
105:**Pivot's approach.** Pivot's BRD articulates role-based access aligned with its divisional sales structure (NBD, Venture, Public, Construction Solutions per CRM §3.02 D-3b) and its in-house operations footprint.
107:**Recommendation for the merged company.** Adopt the standard Orion 25+ custom role taxonomy with merged-company adaptations: roles support both Pivot's divisional structure and KBM's geographic territories per the two-dimensional model locked in CRM §3.02 D-3a. Operations-specific roles reflect Pivot's in-house operations team plus KBM's outsourced-operations coordination roles (per Operations §3.05).
113:### D-5. Historical data migration scope
