_Unification/working/codex-run-v2.log:2092:_Unification/working/codex-run.log:5796:_Unification/working/pivot-brds-md/Marketing.md:115:The NetSuite Orion solution with HubSpot integration addresses Pivot's requirements for automated lead\-to\-opportunity conversion, comprehensive event management with ROI tracking, email marketing automation, lead nurturing workflows, and marketing attribution analytics\. The implementation will establish seamless data flow between marketing and sales systems while preserving HubSpot's sophisticated marketing capabilities and NetSuite's robust ERP functionality\. 
