_Unification/working/codex-run-v2.log:2183:_Unification/working/codex-run.log:6740:5. **D-10 is not stable enough to default.** The pilot defaults to retaining HubSpot with bidirectional sync. Pivot’s CRM BRD does say bidirectional sync in SuiteApps (`CRM.md` lines 531-532), but the Pivot review session later says HubSpot is being kept for marketing only and likely one-directional from Orion to HubSpot (`2026-02-19...` lines 94-98), and Pivot System Setup says HubSpot integration will be explored after go-live (`System_Setup_and_Configuration.md` lines 175-175). This needs to move out of “default yes” territory.
