System Setup and Configuration/KBMH/3 Output/BRD_SystemSetupConfiguration_v1.0.md:355:For payroll integration with Paylocity (or alternative HR platform), NetSuite enables CSV import of journal entries, maintaining financial system integration without requiring the payroll system to store financial detail. This approach accommodates the separation between HRIS and ERP while ensuring financial accuracy.
